{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/HeadAbout.png?t=1733314502\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Oasis</h2>In a world without sun, havens of life like the Oasis has developed around sources of lights. These regions are cut off each from other by wastelands of darkness called Abysses.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/Gif_Ver.gif?t=1733314502\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Dynamic Combat</h2>Combine different weapon types and use your equipment skills to create your playstyle! Attacks, spells and combos are the recipe for dynamic combat that tests your dexterity and imagination! Think about it as a group to take on the toughest challenges!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/Gif_Combat_New.gif?t=1733314502\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Varieties of choice</h2>Unlock a multitude of heroes to try to save the Oasis. Increase their destinies and unlock new ones, as well as numerous equipment.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2666000/extras/Gif_Chara_New.gif?t=1733314502\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Different missions</h2>Adventures taking place in the past will allow you to modify the context of your main quest and achieve your objective... if the temporal balance is not broken.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Versus</h2>Settle your conflicts in a versus mode with the possibility of fighting in 2v2! Upgrade your equipment between each fight and adopt the right strategy to win your revenge!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Traveler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2666000/b361dbcf746639daab1bfa8da559fa9c9338778b.jpg"},{"name":"Lost love","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2666000/95bcb9